'desc': [u'

Pigeon Baby Nail Clippers Yellow Price: Rs.520

Children can become very messy at times and they can get all kinds of dirt on their skin and under the nails. This is one of the reasons that small children’s nails should be regularly trimmed. Long nails on an infant’s hands can also result in them bruising themselves with it. You can use the Pigeon Safety Nail Clipper to safely and perfectly clip your baby’s nails. These Nail Clippers are designed in a very practical keeping in mind the safety requirements.

The corners are rounded to avoid any kind of injury to your bundle of joy’s skin. The blades on the Safety Nail Clipper from Pigeon are small and hence ideal to clip a newborn’s nails safely. Extreme care has been taken to build this Nail Clipper with a perfect angle that curbs paring to a great extent. The handle on this Safety Nail Clipper from Pigeon has a strong grip that will easily fit the clipper in your hand without slipping. Another alluring aspect of this Pigeon Nail Cutter is that the cut nails can be stored inside the trimmer. After cutting all the nails you can just overturn the clipper and store the Nail Clipper in the case. This facility will prevent the nails from being strewn all over the place. It is ideal and safe to trim a baby’s nail when he or she is asleep so that you can prevent the child resisting to cut the nails.

']
